long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sharetute easy bookmark helps you easily create and explore your bookmarks tutorials managed on sharetute.com. With the extension, you can explore any sharetute member directory and go straight to the tutorials. You can also create tutorial cards more easily, the extension will extract the data from the page you are visiting and fill out the form so that you can quickly add a tutorial to your folder.
